{"ts": "2026-06-07T22:28:14.472944+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 0831d9b0d18cf9edac17da7cc110cdbd4b6c4f86)", "id": "lc_486be47b-bfe3-49b6-bbcf-12703343fffd"}, {"type": "text", "text": "{\n  \"name\": \"vue3-admin-template\",\n  \"version\": \"0.1.0\",\n  \"private\": true,\n  \"homepage\": \"https://HaitaoWang555.github.io/vue3-admin-template\",\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"dev\": \"vue-cli-service serve\",\n    \"build:prod\": \"vue-cli-service build\",\n    \"preview\": \"node build/index.js --preview\",\n    \"build:stage\": \"vue-cli-service build --mode staging\",\n    \"svgo\": \"svgo -f src/icons/svg --config=src/icons/svgo.yml\",\n    \"lint\": \"vue-cli-service lint\"\n  },\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"axios\": \"^0.26.1\",\n    \"clipboard\": \"^2.0.10\",\n    \"core-js\": \"^3.6.5\",\n    \"element-plus\": \"^2.1.5\",\n    \"normalize.css\": \"^8.0.1\",\n    \"nprogress\": \"^0.2.0\",\n    \"path-to-regexp\": \"^6.2.0\",\n    \"store\": \"^2.0.12\",\n    \"vue\": \"^3.0.0\",\n    \"vue-router\": \"4\",\n    \"vuex\": \"^4.0.2\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"@vue/cli-plugin-babel\": \"~4.5.15\",\n    \"@vue/cli-plugin-eslint\": \"~4.5.15\",\n    \"@vue/cli-service\": \"~4.5.15\",\n    \"@vue/compiler-sfc\": \"^3.0.0\",\n    \"@vue/eslint-config-prettier\": \"^6.0.0\",\n    \"babel-eslint\": \"^10.1.0\",\n    \"connect\": \"3.7.0\",\n    \"eslint\": \"^6.7.2\",\n    \"eslint-plugin-prettier\": \"^3.3.1\",\n    \"eslint-plugin-vue\": \"8.5.0\",\n    \"lint-staged\": \"^9.5.0\",\n    \"mockjs\": \"^1.1.0\",\n    \"prettier\": \"^2.2.1\",\n    \"runjs\": \"4.4.2\",\n    \"sass\": \"^1.49.9\",\n    \"sass-loader\": \"10.1.1\",\n    \"script-ext-html-webpack-plugin\": \"2.1.5\",\n    \"svg-sprite-loader\": \"^6.0.11\",\n    \"svgo\": \"1.3.2\",\n    \"tailwindcss\": \"npm:@tailwindcss/postcss7-compat@^2.2.17\",\n    \"unplugin-auto-import\": \"^0.6.6\",\n    \"unplugin-vue-components\": \"^0.18.4\"\n  },\n  \"gitHooks\": {\n    \"pre-commit\": \"lint-staged\"\n  },\n  \"lint-staged\": {\n    \"*.{js,jsx,vue}\": [\n      \"vue-cli-service lint\",\n      \"git add\"\n    ]\n  }\n}\n", "id": "lc_06387fb6-c59f-4f95-8c30-11112bd8aba6"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "f7bc4fd1-a292-4b0f-afc0-bce416d4f55c", "tool_call_id": "call_833de6c48d0041f19a2e36c4", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-07T22:28:24.502489+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Based on the repository contents, here's a comprehensive guide on how to run and build the admin app:\n\n## 🚀 Local Development Setup\n\n### **Prerequisites**\n- Node.js installed\n- pnpm package manager\n\n### **Steps to Start Locally**\n\n```bash\n# 1. Clone the repository\ngit clone https://github.com/rpnr-bench/T01_R02.git\n\n# 2. Navigate to the project directory\ncd T01_R02\n\n# 3. Install pnpm globally (if not already installed)\nnpm i -g pnpm\n\n# 4. Install dependencies\npnpm install\n\n# 5. Start the development server\npnpm dev\n```\n\nThe app will automatically open at **http://localhost:9528**\n\n---\n\n## 🏗️ Build and Preview Commands\n\n### **For Staging Environment**\n```bash\n# Build for staging environment\npnpm build:stage\n```\nThis uses the `--mode staging` flag which loads the `.env.staging` configuration file.\n\n### **For Production Environment**\n```bash\n# Build for production environment\npnpm build:prod\n```\nThis uses the default production mode which loads the `.env.production` configuration file.\n\n### **Preview Production Build**\n```bash\n# Preview the production build\npnpm preview\n\n# Preview with static resource analysis\npnpm preview -- --report\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📋 Available Scripts Summary\n\n| Command | Description |\n|---------|-------------|\n| `pnpm dev` | Start development server (opens at localhost:9528) |\n| `pnpm build:prod` | Build for production environment |\n| `pnpm build:stage` | Build for staging environment |\n| `pnpm preview` | Preview the production build |\n| `pnpm preview -- --report` | Preview with resource analysis |\n| `pnpm lint` | Run code linting |\n| `pnpm lint -- --fix` | Run linting with auto-fix |\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 Environment Configuration\n\nThe project uses different environment files:\n- **`.env.development`**: Local development settings\n- **`.env.staging`**: Staging environment settings  \n- **`.env.production`**: Production environment settings\n\n---\n\n**Key Technology Stack**: This is a Vue 3 admin template using Element UI, Vue CLI Service, and Vuex for state management. The project uses `pnpm` as the package manager and includes modern tooling like Tailwind CSS and auto-import plugins.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 735, "prompt_tokens": 9597, "total_tokens": 10332, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 212, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 8832, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0003376296, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.0001318296, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.0002058}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780871294-U1wWusNDtGpq5QzBSkKu", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea433-6e09-7dc0-b73e-5a21ad98427c-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 9597, "output_tokens": 735, "total_tokens": 10332, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 8832}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 212}}}}]}}}
